{"tid":315349,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"董建華家族旗下東方海外賣盤！國企中遠海運492億收購","createTime":"2017-07-10T03:16:20.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-10T04:30:20.000Z","uid":30561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5f8ae20c0d6a832786132db50b39836791e32f14","tid":315349,"uid":30561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T03:16:20.000Z","msg":"董建華家族旗下東方海外賣盤！國企中遠海運492億收購 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170709/large/1499595388_e1a9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170709%2Flarge%2F1499595388_e1a9.jpg&h=4a740df9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n前特首董建華之父董浩雲創辦的香港最大航企東方海外（316）刊出通告，指獲中國遠洋提出全面收購東方海外國際的所有已發行股份，收購總代價為492億元，即每股78.67元，溢價較上周最後收市價高31%。 <br />\n<br />\n董建華家族現時持東方海外約68.7%，董家已承諾賣股，涉資338億元。當中中遠海運要約人收購58.8%，上港集團要約人收購9.9%。 <br />\n<br />\n事實上，自今年初起，市場不停傳出東方海外有賣盤消息，不過該公司卻不斷否認。東方海外年初至今股價已升近1倍，周五收市報60元。 <br />\n<br />\n收購完成前必須符合幾大條件，包括符合中國《反壟斷法》，而中遠海運亦須獲得中國發改委、國務院、國資委等監管機構同意。 <br />\n<br />\n通告指出，全球集裝箱運輸業務是中遠海運下一步發展的戰略重點和核心業務，是未來服務全球客戶的重要平台。本次交易後，聯席要約人有意保留東方海外在香港的上市地位、為香港的航運業提供更大的發展空間，支援香港國際航運中心的發展。東方海外總部及管理職能繼續留在香港，以保證其運作和業務網路的整體持續性和穩定性。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/finance/20170709/56934394\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Ffinance%2F20170709%2F56934394&d=SNSQihyh%2Fj3X1%2BENQWX1JdWu%2BWjcEfCiPsVdizSUn%2FE%3D&h=3735466f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Ffinance%2F20170709%2F56934394&h=111645e1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/finance/20170709/56934394</a>"},{"pid":"655b6dbf347bbf59b5c90c08391f5a53b3c094e2","tid":315349,"uid":69670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T03:35:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e96629f70fc0d6a5ffede643889ac5cdf552f635","tid":315349,"uid":64345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T03:47:00.000Z","msg":"國家出糧了。"},{"pid":"c57352125c13cf629325d1a1df85c83c86e665cd","tid":315349,"uid":53223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T03:48:27.000Z","msg":"愛國愛港就送500億<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2aed85be2d5665e466f7f6002efeaee1fa40b6e","tid":315349,"uid":44171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T03:49:06.000Z","msg":"佢仲要咁多錢做咩? 移民? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f3beb924baf7acfb7cdb85153ab471d2884ca38","tid":315349,"uid":33668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T03:49:16.000Z","msg":"唔算敗家嘅 東方海外正式換d 出到海外嘅資產"},{"pid":"76348ef5196a2d182aed301dd4e15b5da4b2858d","tid":315349,"uid":36502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T03:52:07.000Z","msg":"政治局常委存款（國債）房產（產業權）<br />\n習近平320萬 2套 福州、北京<br />\n李克強295萬 2套 鄭州、北京<br />\n張德江305萬 2套 廣州、北京<br />\n俞正聲540萬 2套 武漢、上海<br />\n劉雲山285萬 2套 承德、北京<br />\n王岐山515萬 1套 北京<br />\n張高麗575萬 2套 濟南、天津<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n董建華！你呢個資本家！點對得住共產黨！"},{"pid":"cd44bea0b533e331b73dcb4f0330e3563c7783c0","tid":315349,"uid":53223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T03:55:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>敗家仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n夕陽行業，賣到500億簡直叻仔啦。如果唔係愛國愛港，國企可以慢慢誅死佢。"},{"pid":"945491390308482730377fe120ccf74a727d0bf6","tid":315349,"uid":38523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T03:58:32.000Z","msg":"又一隻假愛國狗移民lu"},{"pid":"e4bfccef6ed5fa3f0fe3e33df01cb197e9b9886e","tid":315349,"uid":39846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-10T04:24:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>敗家仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n夕陽行業，賣到500億簡直叻仔啦。如果唔係愛國愛港，國企可以慢慢誅死佢。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔好玩啦&hellip;&hellip;&hellip;&hellip; 